[5] [CITE@@en[SMIL 3.0 State]] ([TIME[2008-12-02 00:45:09 +09:00]] 版) <http://www.w3.org/TR/2008/REC-SMIL3-20081201/smil-state.html#StateNS-StateInterpolation>

